reviewText: Thought it would be a concert, but more talking

Worse sound track ever!  Can't distinguish most verbal conversations, just terrible DVD.
Bad thing, I had it a year before I opened package to play and unable to return. UGH>>>

I would not recommend buying this unless you are a diehard fan.  Weird that it is unauthorized.  And the bizarre inaccuracies (he started his "Global Warming" tour in Jan 2012?) make me doubt everything in here that I didn't know before.
